version_description: Bug fixes and some technological improvements.
Even more styles for your creative cartoon portraits!

We've made several improvements. Keep creating your cartoons in a more stable and friendly environment.

Like ToonMe app? Share your feedback in reviews! ;)
Bug fixes and performance improvements
Bug fixes and performance improvements
Extra fun options for better social networking: get ready to cartoon up your snaps and stories!
Cartoons rock! And we do our best to meet your expectations in each update. With minor improvements in this version we anticipate greater changes to come. :)
Everything changes. So does ToonMe! We improve and develop our app every day to make you happier.
Magical? Wowable? Unique? Let’s see what AI will say about you with its extended collection of templates and smarter algorithm under the hood! ;)
We want you to enjoy cartoons even more, so this version brings some bug fixes and minor improvements.
Get ready for even more fun with our brand-new portraits in vector style! Be the very first to apply them and show off your new profile picture in social networks. ;)
Our ToonMe tab has just get cooler, bigger, and more diverse. Check out new styles (including vectors) and play further with layouts to adorn them uniquely.
We needed to do some housework. It's not that you're gonna notice it, but we'd rather you update your ToonMe to this new version. Thanks!
Remember to stay TOONed and get your cartoons ready for Halloween! Find the scary-toon-death effects that match your style and personality.

Oops, we have detected a tiny bug and now you need to update. No worries though, your app will be up and running again in no time. ;)

Also remember to stay TOONed and get your cartoons ready for Halloween! Find the scary-toon-death effects that match your style and personality.
We have made a few under-the-hood changes. You are unlikely to notice them, but the app stability has been improved.
Ready for the most wonderful time of the year? We are! With the most TOON-tastic cartoon and vector templates that will make the coolest Christmas profile pictures ever. Have fun!
We have made a few under-the-hood changes. You are unlikely to notice them, but the app stability has been improved.
We hope ToonMe has already become your secret tool for awesome cartoon and vector selfies! At least we do everything possible to constantly add more styles and effects to our feed. Stay TOONed! ;)
It's time for new arrivals! Totally cool and undoubtedly iconic looks are already inside. As well as many new effects in Feed you are so used to. Stay TOONed!

ToonMe.com is up & running again! We are glad to let you know that all issues arisen from huge demand for our ToonMe.com effects have been fixed. Our servers are now scaled and waiting for your photos.


Sorry for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. We love you to the TOON & back!

We've got new TOONME.COM icon! We loved the old one, but it got to look misleading in comparison to those of some competitors' who is trying hard to impersonate us and make you download the wrong app. So stay TOONed with the original app!

PS. We love you!

Get ready for fresh styles in TOONME.COM tab! Process your photo as usually and then tap the last but one preview in the top carousel. Quick tip: use "Refresh" for even more effects. :)

We love your to the TOON and back!
We want ToonMe to be your little secret key to the coolest cartoons ever, that's why we keep improving it 24/7. Now you know it, update and stay TOONed. ;)
We keep developing ToonMe daily (and sometimes nightly) to deliver the best effects and styles to your devices. Update and stay TOONed for new looks. ;)
